sequenceDiagram
    participant App as App
    participant EE as EventEmitter
    participant L1 as Listener A
    participant L2 as Listener B
    App->>EE: on('progresso', L1)
    App->>EE: on('progresso', L2)
    App->>EE: once('concluido', cleanUp)
    Note over EE: Durante execucao
    App->>EE: emit('progresso', {etapa, percentual})
    EE->>L1: callback({etapa, percentual})
    EE->>L2: callback({etapa, percentual})
    Note over EE: Ao final
    App->>EE: emit('concluido')
    EE->>L1: callback() (apenas 1x)